        <briefdescription>
<para>this routine is a stub for the asynchronous error interrupt callback. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>the stub is here in case the upper layer forgot to set the handler. on initialization, error interrupt handler is set to this callback. it is considered an error for this handler to be invoked.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
